| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6981 — Recovery Inhibition (securotrop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f4ce929e-c840-583d-9269-a644823d1dcf"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
